{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "第十九回 关中九豪。辛捷与吴凌风途经桐柏山，目睹山左双豪（摘星手司空宗、神剑金趁林少皋）打劫杀人，被点苍派掌门落英剑谢长卿出手制止。谢长卿以七绝手法击败林少卿，与司空宗对峙。此时关中九豪成员任卓宣（晓月五更寒心掌）携白风（长天一碧）赶到，揭露关中九豪东山再起的阴谋，并透露谢长卿师弟千手剑客陆方已叛逃加入九豪。谢长卿被四人围攻陷入危境，辛捷蒙面冒充七妙神君出手相助，以寒心掌力硬接任卓宣、林少皋、司空宗三人合力。吴凌风随后加入战团对抗白风。谢长卿面对昔日仇人七妙神君（辛捷），内心十年愧疚翻涌，几欲趁机暗算，最终良知战胜贪念，选择放弃。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "好像是有三个人在交手——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zong",
      "speaker_name": "司空宗",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "阁下真好身手，且接大爷一掌——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zong",
      "text": "山左双豪，武艺通神，怎么来到桐柏山区？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zong",
      "text": "司空兄休得误会，在下姓谢名长卿——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zong",
      "speaker_name": "司空宗",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "想不到阁下竟是点苍掌门落英剑谢大侠！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zong",
      "text": "山左双豪向来讲究义气，这一点谢某人也还深知！但不想二位深山拦劫，且尽诛毫无武技、身无寸铁的老少七口，下手未免过辣一些儿吧？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zong",
      "speaker_name": "司空宗",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "咱们是干此行为活，下手自然重一些，谢老师若是不忍——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zong",
      "text": "说不得，谢某人要请二位赐教了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "长天一点碧，晓月五更寒……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "山左双豪绝艺已然领教，谢某因有急事，先行失陪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "任老英雄，你可也算是成名之人，怎么一再欺骗在下？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "好个落英剑，你们点苍门人自动投入本派，你做掌门人的却尽找咱们麻烦，也不怕叫人耻笑？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "任卓宣老匹夫，可不是谢某有意挑衅，谢某要得罪了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "莫说你们二个，就是头儿一起来，谢某照样接下。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "姓谢的休狂，你仔细听着：关中霸九豪，河洛惟一剑，海内尊七妙，世外有三仙！如今河洛一剑尸寒已久，世外三仙不履中土，七妙神君虽然曾传出现，也只不过传说而已，芸芸武林中，关中九豪已显然成了领袖……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "闲话少说，就算你有海天双煞撑腰又怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "海天二位老前辈已决意再组九霸，重整旗鼓，你听着，海天九霸中除海天双煞及昔年归隐二位，共四位外，外加的五人便是山左双豪，区区在下和长天一碧白兄——还有一个便是你姓谢的师弟，千手剑客陆方陆老弟！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "这可是他自愿的，呶，你看——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "那么那秘笈呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "那是陆老弟的事了，老夫并不知道！姓谢的，你一再挑衅，老夫总是隐忍，不过是想借你这张嘴传遍武林，说关中九豪东山再起，否则动起手来，你还有命吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "今儿却要让你吃点儿苦头，让天下人得知关中九豪不是好惹的，五大宗派仍须臣服在咱们之下——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "谢长卿",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "好说！好说！咱就先来试试九豪的威风！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": "char_xie_chang_qing",
      "text": "姓谢的，你仔细估量估量，咱们四人二前二后对付你，你还要逞强么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "关中九豪怎样？梅某年纪虽老，但是——嘿！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "关中九豪东山再起，就凭你们这一批烂货？老实说，我梅某人第一个就不服，以你们这等功夫便能和区区齐名？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "任卓宣",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "五大剑派的剑下亡魂，还想在武林中重树旗帜么？哈哈——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ren_zhuo_xuan",
      "text": "是又怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    }
  ],
